<li>Professional Conference Managers Assn. — Washington DC — Delivered keynote and chaired industry panel on global trends affecting the conference industry — November 2006.</li>
<li>South Korean Ministry of Culture and Tourism — Seoul, Korea — Principal speaker and panelist in three-day conference on the impact of globalization on Korean tourism. Delivered paper on the impact of new technologies on social and cultural change — March 2007.</li>
